OL,3,CThailand to ban recreational cannabis
OL,4,Cthree years after decriminalisation
OL,6,FThailand is moving to pass new
OL,7,Flegislation banning cannabis for
OL,8,Frecreational use in a major reversal,
OL,9,Fthree years after the country became
OL,10,Fthe first in Asia to decriminalise the
OL,11,Fdrug, local media reports.
OL,13,FOn Tuesday, Public Health Minister
OL,14,FSomsak Thepsuthin said he had signed
OL,15,Fan announcement limiting cannabis to
OL,16,Fmedical use only, Bangkok news site
OL,17,FKhaosod confirmed.
