OL,3,CThailand to ban recreational cannabis
OL,4,Cthree years after decriminalisation
OL,6,FUnder the changes, people wishing to
OL,7,Fpurchase cannabis must have a doctor's
OL,8,Fprescription and a medical certificate
OL,9,Findicating their illness.
OL,11,FOperators selling the drug will need
OL,12,Fto have a doctor present at the shop
OL,13,Fto renew or apply for a license to
OL,14,Fsell.
OL,16,FSomsak also said that in the future,
OL,17,Fcannabis will return to being
OL,18,Fconsidered a narcotic.
