OL,3,CThailand to ban recreational cannabis
OL,4,Cthree years after decriminalisation
OL,6,FIt is not clear when the regulation
OL,7,Fwill take effect or when it will be re-
OL,8,Flisted.
OL,10,FIs cannabis legal in Thailand?
OL,12,FMedical marijuana has been legal in
OL,13,FThailand since 2018, but
OL,14,Fdecriminalisation in 2022 took things
OL,15,Fa step further, making it no longer a
OL,16,Fcrime to grow and trade marijuana and
OL,17,Fhemp products, or to use any parts of
OL,18,Fthe plant to treat illnesses.
