OL,3,CThailand to ban recreational cannabis
OL,4,Cthree years after decriminalisation
OL,6,FIt was a rarity in the region where
OL,7,Fmany countries give long jail terms
OL,8,Fand even death sentences for people
OL,9,Fconvicted of marijuana possession,
OL,10,Fconsumption or trafficking.
OL,12,FSmoking marijuana in public remained
OL,13,Fillegal even under the relaxed laws.
