OL,3,CThailand to ban recreational cannabis
OL,4,Cthree years after decriminalisation
OL,6,FThe relaxed laws saw a lucrative
OL,7,Fcannabis industry catering to locals
OL,8,Fand foreigners alike boom across the
OL,9,FSoutheast Asian nation, with thousands
OL,10,Fof cannabis dispensaries sprouting up
OL,11,Facross Thailand, as well as other
OL,12,Fcannabis-themed businesses like weed
OL,13,Fcafes and hemp spas, and beauty
OL,14,Ftreatment.
OL,16,FCities like Chiang Mai and the capital
OL,17,FBangkok have even held weed festivals,
OL,18,Fand decriminalisation has been a major
OL,19,Fdraw for tourists.
