OL,3,CThailand to ban recreational cannabis
OL,4,Cthree years after decriminalisation
OL,6,FPro-legislation advocates have argued
OL,7,Fthat the cannabis boom across Thailand
OL,8,Fhas helped many Thais, from farmers to
OL,9,Fsmall business owners and workers
OL,10,Fbehind the counter.
OL,12,FCritics say the decriminalisation was
OL,13,Frushed through, causing confusion
OL,14,Fabout the regulations.
OL,16,FLast year, a new conservative
OL,17,Fgovernment vowed to tighten the rules
OL,18,Faround the drug after a string of
OL,19,Falleged smuggling cases involving
OL,20,Ftourists.
